org.hibernate.search.elasticsearch.analyzer.definition

Interface ElasticsearchAnalysisDefinitionRegistryBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ElasticsearchAnalysisDefinitionRegistryBuilderImpl

    public interface ElasticsearchAnalysisDefinitionRegistryBuilder
    A builder for Elasticsearch analysis-related definitions: analyzers, tokenizers, char filters, ...

    This contract only expects users to provide the definitions; the registry building is handled by Hibernate Search.

    Author:
    Yoann Rodiere
    Experimental
    The specific API of this DSL is a prototype. Please let us know what you like and what you don't like, and bear in mind that this will likely change in any future version.

      • analyzer

        ElasticsearchAnalyzerDefinitionContext analyzer(String name)
        Start an analyzer definition.
        Parameters:
        name - The name used to reference this analyzer (both in Elasticsearch and in Hibernate Search).
        Returns:
        The analyzer definition context, allowing to define the analyzer's components (tokenizer, ...).
